videos.description: Virignia's Kyle Guy rises for a jumpshot, but leads Jay Huff instead with a bounce pass for the flush.
videos.headline: Guy drops excellent bouncer to Huff for dunk

videos.description: Torin Dorn displays his athleticism as he drives baseline and gets the crafty reverse lay-in to fall.
videos.headline: Dorn drops wild reverse layup for NC State

videos.description: Braxton Key receives a pass from beyond the 3-point line and quickly lobs it up to Jay Huff, who rises and smashes the and-1 dunk.
videos.headline: Virginia's Huff spikes and-1 alley-oop in OT

videos.description: NC State head coach Kevin Keatts announces to the fans to stop throwing items onto the floor and to cheer for the Wolfpack instead.
videos.headline: Keatts takes mic, insists fans to stop throwing things onto floor

videos.description: NC State's Markell Johnson is fouled on a 3-point attempt with .9 seconds remaining, but would later miss a free throw, giving Virignia the win.
videos.headline: Virginia grinds out victory despite foul on NC State 3-pointer
